description:
The coronavirus (COVID-19) has crippled our economies, shut down our factories and kept us confined to our homes. Here is a message from all of us to this new virus.

Please download the high-resolution version of this video TO PUBLISH ON YOUR OWN CHANNELS. We believe this video will have a profound impact on the world if we all publish it and promote it. 

We are profoundly thankful for the vision and direction of our Inter-European and Trans-European Divisions who produced this video in 48 hours with 32 languages. Here is the link to the original files: https://cloud.eud.adventist.org/index.php/s/5cfgGekmbkiwqCT

The official accounts of the Seventh-day Adventist World Church:
